Package: encodeUtils
Type: Package
Title: Query and Retrieve ENCODE Portal Metadata and Files
Version: 0.99.2
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Zoheb",
    family = "Khan",
    email = "zohebkhan600@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0266-8886")
    )
Description: Provides an R workflow for discovering ENCODE Portal datasets
    through the ENCODE REST API and converting ENCODE JSON metadata into
    analysis-ready tables. Supports scripted searches for RNA-seq, ChIP-seq,
    and ATAC-seq experiments, accession-aware file listing and selection,
    download planning, supported local file readers, and reproducibility
    manifests.
License: Artistic-2.0
URL: https://github.com/ZohebKhan1/encodeUtils, https://zohebkhan1.github.io/encodeUtils/
